name: 00 Memory Card - SARASVATI District
description: After exploring the harsh district (El Dorado) last week, now is the time to set foot in the Sarasvati district, the safest area which is suitable for retirees. It is inhabited by multi-ethnic that makes it is rich with various cultures, beliefs, and unique architecture from all angles. it is easy to find famous and delicious restaurants from Asian to African specialties there. The second most populous district after the main district, Omega.
